source.name: Veterans Affairs Veteran Population Model - County Level Estimates and Projections
source.description: VetPop2007 is VA's latest official estimate and projection of the veteran population and their characteristics from 4/1/2000 to 9/30/2036, projected as of 9/30/2006.  This dataset contains the estimate and projection at the county level by gender and 4 year age group.  There is one record for each unique combination of county, gender and age group with the corresponding number of veterans estimated or projected for each of the years from 4/1/2000 to 9/30/2036.
